'''亚斯码头赛道'''（[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯语]]：حلبة مرسى ياس）是[[一级方程式赛车|一级方程式赛车]][[阿布扎比大奖赛|阿布扎比大奖赛]]的比赛地点。赛道由[[赫尔曼·提尔克|赫尔曼·提尔克]]（Hermann Tilke）所设计，<ref name="tilke">{{cite news | title=Tilke GmbH – Projects – Category | url=http://www.tilke-ac.de/projects.php?projid=1065-02&imgno=1 | publisher=tilke-ac.de | date=2009-10-29 | accessdate=2009-10-30 | archive-date=2016-01-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160120131648/http://www.tilke-ac.de/projects.php?projid=1065-02&imgno=1 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title=Yas Marina Circuit construction progressing | url=http://www.gulfnews.com/Sport/Motor_Racing/10244440.html | publisher=gulfnews.com | date=2009-10-29 | accessdate=2009-10-30 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090129145657/http://www.gulfnews.com/Sport/Motor_Racing/10244440.html | archivedate=2009-01-29 }}</ref>坐落于[[亚斯岛|亚斯岛]]，距离[[阿拉伯联合酋长国|阿拉伯联合酋长国]]首都[[阿布扎比|阿布扎比]]有30分钟的车程。亚斯码头赛道是[[一级方程式赛车|一级方程式赛车]]在[[中东地区|中东地区]]的第二条赛道，第一条赛道是由同一设计者所设计的[[巴林国际赛道|巴林国际赛道]]。赛道开幕的当天官方举办了为期两天的[[GP2亚洲系列赛|GP2亚洲系列赛]]测试赛，一周后进行了[[2009年阿布扎比大奖赛|2009年阿布扎比大奖赛]]。<ref>{{cite news | title = GP2 race will officially open Yas Marina Circuit | work = Gulf News | publisher = Al Nisr Publishing | url = http://www.gulfnews.com/sport/Motor_Racing/10339863.html | date = 2009-08-12 | accessdate = 2009-08-12 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090815231558/http://www.gulfnews.com/sport/Motor_Racing/10339863.html | archivedate = 2009-08-15 }}</ref>赛道并于2010年2月举行了{{link-en|V8超级房车赛|V8 Supercars}}的揭幕战，{{link-en|亚斯 V8 400|Yas V8 400}}大奖赛。<ref>{{cite news | title=Motorsport: Middle Eastern double-header for V8 Supercars | url=http://www.nzherald.co.nz/motoring/news/article.cfm?c_id=9&objectid=10596444 | publisher=nzherald.co.nz | date=2009-10-29 | accessdate=2009-10-30 | archive-date=2012-10-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021070441/http://www.nzherald.co.nz/motoring/news/article.cfm?c_id=9&objectid=10596444 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Abu Dhabi start confirmed |url=http://www.v8supercars.com.au/content/hero_news/september_2009/abu_dhabi_start_confirmed/ |publisher=v8supercars.com.au |date=2009-10-29 |accessdate=2009-10-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5jjr3ycHf?url=http://www.v8supercars.com.au/content/hero_news/september_2009/abu_dhabi_start_confirmed/ |archivedate=2009-09-12 }}</ref>

==设计==
[[File:YasMarina1.jpeg|180px]]
[[File:YasMarina2.jpeg|180px]]

赛道共设计有21个弯角，从亚斯岛蜿蜒贯穿至阿布扎比海滩，<ref>{{cite news|title=Motorsport: Abu Dhabi debut marks F1 driver shake-up | url = http://www.nzherald.co.nz/motorsport/news/article.cfm?c_id=66&objectid=10606047 | publisher = nzherald.co.nz | date = 2009-10-29 | accessdate = 2009-10-30}} {{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>其中经过了船坞并穿过了由[[纽约|纽约]]建筑师{{link-en|哈尼·拉希德|Hani Rashid}}和{{link-en|丽莎·安妮·康特尔|Lise Anne Couture}}构思并设计的{{link-en|阿布扎比亚斯总督酒店|Yas Viceroy Abu Dhabi Hotel}}，酒店与赛道由几条长直路和急弯与沙丘相互蜿蜒的结合。

在[[船坞|船坞]]周边开发的建筑包括[[主题公园|主题公园]]、[[水上乐园|水上乐园]]，以及住宅区、酒店和海滩。

赛道有五个大看台区（主看台、西看台、北看台、南看台以及滨海看台），维修通道的出口位于赛道的下方。维修区的后方建造有媒体中心、高速赛车轨道、贵宾楼和[[法拉利世界主题公园|法拉利世界主题公园]]<ref name="Yas Marina">{{cite journal |date=October 2008 |title=Abu Dhabi breaks cover |journal=[[Autosport|Autosport]] |volume=194 |issue=4 |pages=10 |accessdate=2008-10-24}}</ref>。此外，其中一个沙砾缓冲区建在西看台的下方。

